[{"Code":"en","Title":"JeniusPay","Slug":"jeniuspay","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"f4d790ea-3efc-48f1-b5a4-3fb111ef56bd\"><img data-block-id=\"3650b61c-648e-4023-9a73-0c096685d4e3\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(56).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" title=\"image(56).png\" width=\"293\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:293px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"941121cb-9c11-440f-bbfb-b92a5a5b6535\">JeniusPay is an innovative digital payment solution from one of Indonesia's leading digital banking platforms. It’s developed by Bank BTPN as part of their Jenius digital banking ecosystem, known for serving tech-savvy urban professionals with modern banking and payment solutions.</p><p data-block-id=\"6602d834-7c51-4ecd-a265-c0405aaf3174\">When customers select JeniusPay at checkout, they can complete the payment either by logging into their Jenius account directly on your checkout page, or by opening their Jenius app and authorizing the payment through the app's interface. The payment is confirmed instantly once the customer verifies the transaction using their Jenius PIN or biometric authentication.</p><hr class=\"hr-divider1\"><h2 data-block-id=\"6146dcc6-4245-4158-a034-de0971f8c50b\">Features</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"556\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:556px;width:556px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:299px;\"><col style=\"width:257px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"4e088b86-37ac-4776-b84f-dd6d39e2aea0\"><strong>Channel code</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"c1a27eec-6e9e-445c-90f7-8f8e41f5ed37\"><code>JENIUSPAY</code></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"4f2ea4d4-680e-4d5c-8dd7-057cecd07eaf\"><strong>Currency</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"31ac9605-1bdc-4cbf-a25a-00d8db02b51f\">IDR</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"7163f18c-77a2-4078-8274-89aa8062b8c5\"><strong>Minimum amount</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"08dff6f0-c8e8-4d4a-9930-9029f764044d\">1,000</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"681c564b-7965-497e-9bd8-ba6f8e63c613\"><strong>Maximum amount</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"b4126a22-e2d0-4b86-9a00-8c932104420b\">20,000,000</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"caf73f49-a61e-4333-933c-584c4df5effc\"><strong>User approval flow</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"8c851427-323e-401e-915a-282702ea649e\">REDIRECT</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"8c6408ce-b70a-4ffc-9422-e3dcd2faf092\"><strong>Save</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"55c82a2f-2d56-4b0e-8965-b213682d3ee6\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"de2a25b8-08c7-4eec-a078-e6547f1b8de9\"><strong>Recurring</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"8f491d6f-618f-4a6e-bf2b-b978701dc8a6\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"74285440-bcb0-429e-ba78-1d70041d91b9\"><strong>Auth &amp; capture</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"b2e9153c-be4e-470a-9946-ba78dd880500\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"05c3b4a5-b514-4306-88c9-fc384e2f106d\"><strong>Partial capture</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"13d03184-a975-49b5-9da7-daa104d7e0ce\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"a29fcbb2-0180-481c-aa66-f57f6c15b07a\"><strong>Multiple partial capture</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"6c8b57fd-bb3a-4487-a890-6cb739b6efed\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"94615c9a-dfd5-426e-ba40-b62292620afa\"><strong>Payment request expiry</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"392767be-b946-400e-8dbc-f0829a5a48c8\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"ce9c50c0-5830-4886-af8e-e1ddcac28dba\"><strong>Payment token validity</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"9ddd87b3-b9f0-41f5-ab84-f5f59cb1a01b\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"2bc27740-ed1d-4831-b79f-9780023597b8\"><strong>Settlement time</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"0728b2aa-fee1-4d92-821f-efcd78b979d1\">T+2 working days</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"c335fe6e-4dec-4cf2-a608-73a2f6bd651f\"><strong>Refund</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"c7fa3e0f-7c67-4eed-bd25-edc604dd3242\">✅</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"207af873-a926-49a3-b6a7-08f9283b02d5\"><strong>Partial refund</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"4ef62033-0481-437c-bcff-75ad1da8be10\">✅</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"0854e2c9-a187-4cea-bbf0-4dfe24ecc651\"><strong>Multiple partial refund</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"00188702-ec0d-4297-a4bf-f23a6a057d29\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"c5965f09-c195-4153-9c5c-709d0f24c5da\"><strong>Refund validity</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"78c4a689-2a7f-44dc-8461-768ce4503220\">0 days</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"14656f4d-3e78-475e-83a1-1d60073c45d7\"><strong>Compatible integration</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"98921ac7-3208-4f7f-8339-54fbb1c07622\">Payment API, Payment Links</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"cb8e0b97-18b4-4de6-b01b-b757a46b1932\">Payment flow</h2><p data-block-id=\"2b8ea8f7-b006-4c90-aec6-78e6b994b1b1\"><img data-block-id=\"68d232b9-86aa-41f6-8cc0-e1488a8f60fa\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(59).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" title=\"image(59).png\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"a7c24f69-40d9-413c-82f5-c293cc9e9bef\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/BgIKVWxEJlM\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" title=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" style=\"display:flex;margin-right:auto;width:640px;height:360px;\"></iframe></p>","SeoTitle":"JeniusPay","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"JeniusPay","Slug":"jeniuspay-e-wallets","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"f4d790ea-3efc-48f1-b5a4-3fb111ef56bd\"><img data-block-id=\"3650b61c-648e-4023-9a73-0c096685d4e3\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(56).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" title=\"image(56).png\" width=\"293\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:293px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"941121cb-9c11-440f-bbfb-b92a5a5b6535\">JeniusPay adalah solusi pembayaran digital inovatif dari salah satu platform perbankan digital terkemuka di Indonesia. JeniusPay dikembangkan oleh Bank BTPN sebagai bagian dari ekosistem perbankan digital Jenius mereka, yang dikenal melayani para profesional perkotaan yang melek teknologi dengan solusi perbankan dan pembayaran modern.</p><p data-block-id=\"6602d834-7c51-4ecd-a265-c0405aaf3174\">Saat pelanggan memilih JeniusPay di halaman checkout, mereka dapat menyelesaikan pembayaran baik dengan masuk ke akun Jenius mereka langsung di halaman checkout Anda, atau dengan membuka aplikasi Jenius mereka dan mengotorisasi pembayaran melalui antarmuka aplikasi. Pembayaran dikonfirmasi secara instan setelah pelanggan memverifikasi transaksi menggunakan PIN Jenius atau otentikasi biometrik mereka.</p><hr class=\"hr-divider1\"><h2 data-block-id=\"6146dcc6-4245-4158-a034-de0971f8c50b\">Fitur</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"556\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:556px;width:556px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:299px;\"><col style=\"width:257px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"4e088b86-37ac-4776-b84f-dd6d39e2aea0\"><strong>Kode channel</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"c1a27eec-6e9e-445c-90f7-8f8e41f5ed37\"><code>JENIUSPAY</code></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"4f2ea4d4-680e-4d5c-8dd7-057cecd07eaf\"><strong>Mata uang</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"31ac9605-1bdc-4cbf-a25a-00d8db02b51f\">IDR</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"7163f18c-77a2-4078-8274-89aa8062b8c5\"><strong>Jumlah minimum</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"08dff6f0-c8e8-4d4a-9930-9029f764044d\">1,000</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"681c564b-7965-497e-9bd8-ba6f8e63c613\"><strong>Jumlah maksimum</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"b4126a22-e2d0-4b86-9a00-8c932104420b\">20,000,000</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"caf73f49-a61e-4333-933c-584c4df5effc\"><strong>Alur persetujuan pengguna</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"8c851427-323e-401e-915a-282702ea649e\">REDIRECT</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"8c6408ce-b70a-4ffc-9422-e3dcd2faf092\"><strong>Simpan</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"55c82a2f-2d56-4b0e-8965-b213682d3ee6\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"de2a25b8-08c7-4eec-a078-e6547f1b8de9\"><strong>Berulang</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"8f491d6f-618f-4a6e-bf2b-b978701dc8a6\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"74285440-bcb0-429e-ba78-1d70041d91b9\"><strong>Auth &amp; capture</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"b2e9153c-be4e-470a-9946-ba78dd880500\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"05c3b4a5-b514-4306-88c9-fc384e2f106d\"><strong>Partial capture</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"13d03184-a975-49b5-9da7-daa104d7e0ce\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"a29fcbb2-0180-481c-aa66-f57f6c15b07a\"><strong>Multiple partial capture</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"6c8b57fd-bb3a-4487-a890-6cb739b6efed\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"94615c9a-dfd5-426e-ba40-b62292620afa\"><strong>Kedaluwarsa permintaan pembayaran</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"392767be-b946-400e-8dbc-f0829a5a48c8\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"ce9c50c0-5830-4886-af8e-e1ddcac28dba\"><strong>Validitas token pembayaran</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"9ddd87b3-b9f0-41f5-ab84-f5f59cb1a01b\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"2bc27740-ed1d-4831-b79f-9780023597b8\"><strong>Waktu settlement</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"0728b2aa-fee1-4d92-821f-efcd78b979d1\">T+2 hari kerja</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"c335fe6e-4dec-4cf2-a608-73a2f6bd651f\"><strong>Refund</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"c7fa3e0f-7c67-4eed-bd25-edc604dd3242\">✅</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"207af873-a926-49a3-b6a7-08f9283b02d5\"><strong>Partial refund</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"4ef62033-0481-437c-bcff-75ad1da8be10\">✅</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"0854e2c9-a187-4cea-bbf0-4dfe24ecc651\"><strong>Multiple partial refund</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"00188702-ec0d-4297-a4bf-f23a6a057d29\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"c5965f09-c195-4153-9c5c-709d0f24c5da\"><strong>Validitas refund</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"78c4a689-2a7f-44dc-8461-768ce4503220\">0 hari</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"14656f4d-3e78-475e-83a1-1d60073c45d7\"><strong>Integrasi yang kompatibel</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"98921ac7-3208-4f7f-8339-54fbb1c07622\">Payment API, Payment Links</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"cb8e0b97-18b4-4de6-b01b-b757a46b1932\">Alur pembayaran</h2><p data-block-id=\"2b8ea8f7-b006-4c90-aec6-78e6b994b1b1\"><img data-block-id=\"68d232b9-86aa-41f6-8cc0-e1488a8f60fa\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(59).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" title=\"image(59).png\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"a7c24f69-40d9-413c-82f5-c293cc9e9bef\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/BgIKVWxEJlM\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" title=\"\" style=\"display:flex;margin-right:auto;width:640px;height:360px;\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\"></iframe></p>","SeoTitle":"JeniusPay","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"JeniusPay","Slug":"jeniuspay-e-wallets","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"f4d790ea-3efc-48f1-b5a4-3fb111ef56bd\"><img data-block-id=\"3650b61c-648e-4023-9a73-0c096685d4e3\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(56).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" title=\"image(56).png\" width=\"293\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:293px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"941121cb-9c11-440f-bbfb-b92a5a5b6535\">JeniusPay เป็นโซลูชันการชำระเงินดิจิทัลที่เป็นนวัตกรรมใหม่จากหนึ่งในแพลตฟอร์มธนาคารดิจิทัลชั้นนำของอินโดนีเซีย พัฒนาโดย Bank BTPN ซึ่งเป็นส่วนหนึ่งของระบบนิเวศธนาคารดิจิทัล Jenius ที่เป็นที่รู้จักในการให้บริการแก่คนทำงานในเมืองที่เชี่ยวชาญด้านเทคโนโลยีด้วยโซลูชันการธนาคารและการชำระเงินที่ทันสมัย</p><p data-block-id=\"6602d834-7c51-4ecd-a265-c0405aaf3174\">เมื่อลูกค้าเลือก JeniusPay ตอนชำระเงิน พวกเขาสามารถชำระเงินให้เสร็จสิ้นได้โดยการเข้าสู่ระบบบัญชี Jenius ของตนโดยตรงบนหน้าชำระเงินของคุณ หรือโดยการเปิดแอป Jenius และอนุมัติการชำระเงินผ่านอินเทอร์เฟซของแอป การชำระเงินจะได้รับการยืนยันทันทีเมื่อลูกค้ายืนยันธุรกรรมโดยใช้ PIN ของ Jenius หรือการยืนยันตัวตนด้วยข้อมูลชีวภาพ</p><hr class=\"hr-divider1\"><h2 data-block-id=\"6146dcc6-4245-4158-a034-de0971f8c50b\">คุณสมบัติ</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"556\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:556px;width:556px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:299px;\"><col style=\"width:257px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"4e088b86-37ac-4776-b84f-dd6d39e2aea0\"><strong>รหัสช่องทาง</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"c1a27eec-6e9e-445c-90f7-8f8e41f5ed37\"><code>JENIUSPAY</code></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"4f2ea4d4-680e-4d5c-8dd7-057cecd07eaf\"><strong>สกุลเงิน</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"31ac9605-1bdc-4cbf-a25a-00d8db02b51f\">IDR</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"7163f18c-77a2-4078-8274-89aa8062b8c5\"><strong>จำนวนเงินขั้นต่ำ</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"08dff6f0-c8e8-4d4a-9930-9029f764044d\">1,000</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"681c564b-7965-497e-9bd8-ba6f8e63c613\"><strong>จำนวนเงินสูงสุด</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"b4126a22-e2d0-4b86-9a00-8c932104420b\">20,000,000</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"caf73f49-a61e-4333-933c-584c4df5effc\"><strong>ขั้นตอนการอนุมัติโดยผู้ใช้</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"8c851427-323e-401e-915a-282702ea649e\">REDIRECT</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"8c6408ce-b70a-4ffc-9422-e3dcd2faf092\"><strong>บันทึก</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"55c82a2f-2d56-4b0e-8965-b213682d3ee6\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"de2a25b8-08c7-4eec-a078-e6547f1b8de9\"><strong>การชำระเงินแบบประจำ</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"8f491d6f-618f-4a6e-bf2b-b978701dc8a6\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"74285440-bcb0-429e-ba78-1d70041d91b9\"><strong>การอนุมัติและการเก็บเงิน</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"b2e9153c-be4e-470a-9946-ba78dd880500\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"05c3b4a5-b514-4306-88c9-fc384e2f106d\"><strong>การเก็บเงินบางส่วน</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"13d03184-a975-49b5-9da7-daa104d7e0ce\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"a29fcbb2-0180-481c-aa66-f57f6c15b07a\"><strong>การเก็บเงินบางส่วนหลายครั้ง</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"6c8b57fd-bb3a-4487-a890-6cb739b6efed\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"94615c9a-dfd5-426e-ba40-b62292620afa\"><strong>การหมดอายุของคำขอชำระเงิน</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"392767be-b946-400e-8dbc-f0829a5a48c8\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"ce9c50c0-5830-4886-af8e-e1ddcac28dba\"><strong>ความถูกต้องของโทเค็นการชำระเงิน</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"9ddd87b3-b9f0-41f5-ab84-f5f59cb1a01b\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"2bc27740-ed1d-4831-b79f-9780023597b8\"><strong>ระยะเวลาการชำระบัญชี</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"0728b2aa-fee1-4d92-821f-efcd78b979d1\">T+2 วันทำการ</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"c335fe6e-4dec-4cf2-a608-73a2f6bd651f\"><strong>การคืนเงิน</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"c7fa3e0f-7c67-4eed-bd25-edc604dd3242\">✅</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"207af873-a926-49a3-b6a7-08f9283b02d5\"><strong>การคืนเงินบางส่วน</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"4ef62033-0481-437c-bcff-75ad1da8be10\">✅</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"0854e2c9-a187-4cea-bbf0-4dfe24ecc651\"><strong>การคืนเงินบางส่วนหลายครั้ง</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"00188702-ec0d-4297-a4bf-f23a6a057d29\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"c5965f09-c195-4153-9c5c-709d0f24c5da\"><strong>ระยะเวลาการคืนเงิน</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"78c4a689-2a7f-44dc-8461-768ce4503220\">0 วัน</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"14656f4d-3e78-475e-83a1-1d60073c45d7\"><strong>การผสานระบบที่เข้ากันได้</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"98921ac7-3208-4f7f-8339-54fbb1c07622\">Payment API, Payment Links</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"cb8e0b97-18b4-4de6-b01b-b757a46b1932\">ขั้นตอนการชำระเงิน</h2><p data-block-id=\"2b8ea8f7-b006-4c90-aec6-78e6b994b1b1\"><img data-block-id=\"68d232b9-86aa-41f6-8cc0-e1488a8f60fa\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(59).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt title=\"image(59).png\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"a7c24f69-40d9-413c-82f5-c293cc9e9bef\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/BgIKVWxEJlM\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" title style=\"display:flex;margin-right:auto;width:640px;height:360px;\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\"></iframe></p><style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style>","SeoTitle":"JeniusPay","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"JeniusPay","Slug":"jeniuspay","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"f4d790ea-3efc-48f1-b5a4-3fb111ef56bd\"><img data-block-id=\"3650b61c-648e-4023-9a73-0c096685d4e3\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(56).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt title=\"image(56).png\" width=\"293\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:293px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"941121cb-9c11-440f-bbfb-b92a5a5b6535\">JeniusPay es una solución de Pago digital innovadora de una de las principales plataformas de banca digital de Indonesia. Fue desarrollada por Bank BTPN como parte de su ecosistema de banca digital Jenius, conocido por atender a profesionales urbanos expertos en tecnología con soluciones modernas de banca y Pago.</p><p data-block-id=\"6602d834-7c51-4ecd-a265-c0405aaf3174\">Cuando los Clientes seleccionan JeniusPay al finalizar la compra (checkout), pueden completar el Pago iniciando sesión en su Cuenta Jenius directamente en su página de checkout, o abriendo su aplicación Jenius y autorizando el Pago a través de la interfaz de la aplicación. El Pago se confirma instantáneamente una vez que el Cliente verifica la Transacción utilizando su PIN Jenius o autenticación biométrica.</p><hr class=\"hr-divider1\"><h2 data-block-id=\"6146dcc6-4245-4158-a034-de0971f8c50b\">Características</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"556\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:556px;width:556px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:299px;\"><col style=\"width:257px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"4e088b86-37ac-4776-b84f-dd6d39e2aea0\"><strong>Código del Canal</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"c1a27eec-6e9e-445c-90f7-8f8e41f5ed37\"><code>JENIUSPAY</code></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"4f2ea4d4-680e-4d5c-8dd7-057cecd07eaf\"><strong>Moneda</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"31ac9605-1bdc-4cbf-a25a-00d8db02b51f\">IDR</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"7163f18c-77a2-4078-8274-89aa8062b8c5\"><strong>Monto mínimo</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"08dff6f0-c8e8-4d4a-9930-9029f764044d\">1,000</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"681c564b-7965-497e-9bd8-ba6f8e63c613\"><strong>Monto máximo</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"b4126a22-e2d0-4b86-9a00-8c932104420b\">20,000,000</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"caf73f49-a61e-4333-933c-584c4df5effc\"><strong>Flujo de aprobación del Cliente</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"257\"><p data-block-id=\"8c851427-323e-401e-915a-282702ea649e\">REDIRECT</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"8c6408ce-b70a-4f